# Move the cursor to the 2nd line (the longest).
# Then move the cursor at the end of the line.
run observe=(view, pos)
key down
key ctrl+e
----
-- view:
â”ƒ  1 hello, world!                      â¤
â”ƒ  2 isn't it a nice day?[7m [0m              â¤
